river-adventure-house.jpg.description: There is a small blue elephant-shaped water feature/slide in the children's pool area. This appears to be designed to look like a whale or elephant with water spraying from it. It's located in the smaller wading pool section near the main building, separate from the larger swimming pool. The feature is blue in color and appears to be a decorative element that sprays water for children to play with.

construction-evening.jpg.description: In the background of the image, there is a small silhouetted figure riding a horse on top of a hill against the dark blue night sky. The scene is placed between the construction site and the castle on the hilltop. The figure and horse appear as a dark outline against the moonlit sky, with trees visible around them.

The castle appears in the top right corner of the image, perched on a hilltop. It's a medieval-style fortress with multiple towers and crenellated walls, shown against a dark blue night sky with a crescent moon nearby. The castle has a reddish-orange glow coming from some of its windows, suggesting it's illuminated from within. It's surrounded by autumn-colored trees on the hillside.

kf-winter.jpg.description: The sun appears in the top right corner of the image as a simple orange circle in a light grey sky with scattered clouds. It's a minimalist illustration style consistent with the rest of the winter scene drawing.

There is a yellow/orange colored log cabin or warming hut located in the middle-lower portion of the image. It appears to be a simple structure with a sloped green roof and is surrounded by people gathered outside. The cabin seems to be a gathering point or rest area for the winter activities taking place on the snowy hillside. There are benches or tables visible outside the cabin where people are congregating.

construction-site.jpg.description: I can see a small fox character in the bottom left portion of the image. It appears to be part of some street art or a mural painted on a wall. The fox character has an exaggerated smiling expression and appears to be drawn in a cartoon style with orange/reddish coloring. It's located near where someone is holding an umbrella, and appears to be part of a larger decorative wall painting.

There is a large green concrete mixer truck in the left portion of the image. The truck has a distinctive rotating drum in green color and is positioned near a construction site area. The mixer drum is shown in its characteristic cylindrical shape with spiral mixing blades visible on its exterior. The truck appears to be actively working at the construction site, with construction workers nearby.

construction-snow.jpg.description: Santa Claus can be found in the upper right portion of the image, wearing his traditional red suit. He appears to be standing near a yellow-green building, possibly a community center or shop. He seems to be interacting with some children near the building's entrance. Santa is depicted in a cartoonish style consistent with the rest of the illustration's winter scene.

There is a red sedan visible in the lower right portion of the image. The car appears to have slid off the snowy road and is partially stuck in snow. It's a small passenger car with a typical sedan body style, colored in bright red. The car is positioned at an angle, suggesting it may have skidded in the winter conditions. There are people nearby and what appears to be some kind of shelter or structure behind it.

mitgutsch-beach.jpg.description: There is a black pirate flag (Jolly Roger) with the classic skull and crossbones design visible near the top center of the image, just below the 'HOTEL' sign. The flag appears to be mounted on what looks like part of a beach or poolside structure in this busy beach/resort scene.

mitgutsch-carnival.jpg.description: There is a small white chef's hat being worn by what appears to be a vendor or food seller in the middle-right portion of the image. The person wearing the hat is standing near what looks like a food stall or counter area. The hat is the traditional tall white toque style typically associated with chefs.

mitgutsch-fight.jpg.description: In the far right upper portion of the chaotic scene, there is a man waving a white flag or surrendering. He's wearing what appears to be blue clothing and is positioned near the green paneled wall. He's surrounded by the general mayhem of the room, with other figures nearby also in various states of distress or motion.

mitgutsch-orchestra.jpg.description: I don't see a mandarin orange in this image. The image shows an orchestra or symphony with many musicians playing various instruments including strings (violins, cellos, bass), woodwinds (clarinets, flutes), brass instruments (trumpets, tubas), percussion, harp, and piano. The scene is set on a wooden stage or floor with warm lighting, but there is no mandarin orange visible anywhere in the scene.

mitgutsch-pirate.jpg.description: I can see a couple kissing in one of the small boats in the turquoise water, located in the right middle section of the image. The couple appears as cartoon characters in a whimsical illustration style, matching the overall pirate/seafaring theme of the image. They are shown in a small round boat, and their romantic moment stands out among the busy, chaotic activities happening all around them in this bustling harbor scene.

mitgutsch-pool.jpg.description: There appears to be a tennis racket on the ground near the bottom left portion of the image, near the base of the water slide structure. It's lying on the grass among some other recreational equipment and children's toys in that area.

mitgutsch-townsquare.jpg.description: There is a small blue kite visible in the upper left portion of the image, flying above the trees. It appears to be a simple diamond-shaped kite with a tail streaming behind it. The kite is being flown in what seems to be a busy street or plaza scene with many people around.

mitgutsch-water.jpg.description: I can see what appears to be a red lobster being hauled up from one of the fishing boats in the harbor. It's located in the lower middle portion of the image, being pulled up from the water by someone on a small wooden fishing boat. The lobster appears to be dangling from some kind of rope or fishing line against the turquoise-colored water background.

tigertom-park3.jpg.description: In the center of the image, there is a yellow and black striped cartoon tiger standing upright on the paved pathway. The tiger appears to be interacting with some children on the wooden walkway/bridge. The tiger's stripes are clearly visible, and it appears to be standing in a friendly, welcoming pose. It's positioned near where several paths intersect in the playground scene.

The soccer ball is located in the bottom portion of the image, being kicked around by children playing a game of soccer. It appears to be a classic black and white soccer ball in motion on the grass field. The ball is positioned between two players who are actively engaged in the game, with one player about to kick it while others are running nearby to join the play.

professions-intersection.jpg.description: There appears to be a small green cactus in a pot being carried on a serving tray by one of the rabbit/bunny characters on the left side of the street. The bunny is one of two gray bunnies carrying food items on trays, likely heading towards the 'EAT ME' café in the scene.

tigertom-intersection.jpg.description: I do not see any cartoon tiger in this image. The image shows a busy street scene with various people, vehicles, and buildings. There are some artwork frames on the blue building wall showing hot air balloons and what appear to be other decorative images, but no tigers. The scene includes cars, a yellow school bus, pedestrians crossing the street, cyclists, and people going about their daily activities, but no tiger characters.

There is a yellow school bus or shuttle bus located in the middle-right portion of the image. The bus is facing right and appears to be at a bus stop with a green shelter/awning. It is stopped at a pedestrian crossing with white stripes on the road. There appears to be people getting on or off the bus. The bus has a distinctive boxy shape typical of school buses and is painted in a bright yellow color.

whodoeswhat-city2.jpg.description: There appears to be a saxophone being played by a person in black clothing near the bottom right section of the image, close to the playground area. The person is standing on the grass while holding the brass-colored instrument.

There is a red fire truck with an extended ladder in the middle-right portion of the image. It appears to be near a construction site where a blue excavator is working. The fire truck is parked on the street and has a distinctive silver/grey ladder extending from its top. It's a traditional style fire engine in bright red coloring.

montreal-snow.jpg.description: There is a brown bear visible in the upper left portion of the image. The bear is standing among the winter scene near some trees and rocks. It appears to be observing the winter activities taking place in the park. Several small red birds and squirrels are visible near the bear. The bear is drawn in the same illustration style as the rest of the scene, with a simple but clear design showing its brown fur and typical bear shape.
